    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">What does he get in return?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-2eeb4fb7-0a62-4efd-9617-87957c909b09" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-06-23/debates/ed1bd9f2-d4e7-434b-aacf-94b2e5e44f50/Clause14%E2%80%94(ChargeOfIncomeTaxFor1949%E2%80%9350)#contribution-2eeb4fb7-0a62-4efd-9617-87957c909b09">
