<p class="">How much does the hon. Gentleman suggest should be knocked off the standard rate for that purpose?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-0c43a941-e514-418d-8d73-c6511e95c710" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
