<p class="">At the moment I am speaking in relation to a reduction to achieve a particular object. I am taking advantage of this Amendment in order to make these points, as another opportunity may not be available to me at a later stage.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
