        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-43b19478-c544-475c-8671-953f379ae601">
                Mr. Fletcher
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-43b19478-c544-475c-8671-953f379ae601" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-06-23/debates/ed1bd9f2-d4e7-434b-aacf-94b2e5e44f50/Clause14%E2%80%94(ChargeOfIncomeTaxFor1949%E2%80%9350)#contribution-43b19478-c544-475c-8671-953f379ae601">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">That is perfectly true. Confidence is not a thing which can be canalised and retained inside the sterling area. This lack of confidence plays just <span id="492" class="column-number" data-column-number="492"></span> as big a rôle in the dollar area. If there were greater confidence in the dollar area about sterling, it would be very much easier for us to sell our goods there. One of the main reasons why we cannot sell our goods was instanced in the speech made by the President of the Board of Trade in Canada. One of my friends wrote to me from there saying, "He has come over here and he has criticised the country for having to be brought up to date much more, saying that that would no doubt bring lower prices." What happened in the minds of the buyer?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-43b19478-c544-475c-8671-953f379ae601" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-06-23/debates/ed1bd9f2-d4e7-434b-aacf-94b2e5e44f50/Clause14%E2%80%94(ChargeOfIncomeTaxFor1949%E2%80%9350)#contribution-43b19478-c544-475c-8671-953f379ae601">
