            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ccf8da4f-1322-4221-a2a6-8bec3e1edbbf" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1949-06-23/debates/ed1bd9f2-d4e7-434b-aacf-94b2e5e44f50/Clause14%E2%80%94(ChargeOfIncomeTaxFor1949%E2%80%9350)#contribution-ccf8da4f-1322-4221-a2a6-8bec3e1edbbf">
