        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-ffd49047-aca6-4c29-b78b-0beb4babe4f7">
                The Economic Secretary to the Treasury (Mr. Douglas Jay)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ffd49047-aca6-4c29-b78b-0beb4babe4f7" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
