<p class="">Is my hon. Friend dissociating himself from the remarks of the hon. Member for East Coventry relating to those people in the United States Congress who are trying to cut down Marshall Aid?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
