an, W. (Maryhill)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Blenkinsop, A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Delargy, H. J.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hardman, D. R.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Blyton, W. R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Dobbie, W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hardy, E. A.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Bowden, Fig. Offr. H. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Dodds, N. N.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Harrison, J.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Braddock, Mrs. E. M. (L'pl. Exch'ge)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Donovan, T.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hastings, Dr. Somerville</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Braddock, T. (Mitcham)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Driberg, T. E. N.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Haworth, J.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Bramall, E. A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Dugdale, J. (W. Bromwich)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Henderson, Joseph (Ardwick)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Brook, D. (Halifax)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Dumpleton, C. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hobson, C. R.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Brooks, T. J. (Rothwell)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Edwards, W. J. (Whitechapel)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Holman, P.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Broughton, Dr. A. D. D.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Evans, Albert (Islington, W.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Holmes, H. E. (Hemsworth)</td></p><p class