<p class="">No, a good case.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6fdefaf1-c8b0-4836-9176-6b2b97bc4e6f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
